s redundant.","BlockStatement","redundantNestedBlock","no-unreachable","Unreachable code.","unreachableCode",["101"],["102"],"'schemaMatches' is defined but never used.","'Typography' is defined but never used.","'schema' is assigned a value but never used.","jsx-a11y/alt-text","img elements must have an alt prop, either with meaningful text, or an empty string for decorative images.","no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation"]